data.description: 4 bed 3 bath on 3.17 acres in the highly desirable Swiss Colony neighborhood located less than 5 miles from Helen. Roof, gutters, HVAC, generator, hardwoods and carpets and fixtures are are less than 3 years old. Downstairs there is a one bedroom one bath mother in law suite with a private entrance and its own private porch. The main level has 2 porches to relax and enjoy the views with a full bath and master on main. Upstairs are 2 large bedrooms with a full bath and a balcony that overlooks the property. The 3.17 acres is easy to maintain with minimal work needed.
